Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.03,0:01:00.83,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Ano machi mukatta bokura
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.83,0:01:05.54,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Detarame na uta wo utai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.54,0:01:09.42,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}“nan da yo, sore” tte warau
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.42,0:01:14.17,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Tabi wa tsuzuku to omotta
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.73,0:01:29.19,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Kanashimi ga tsuzuku michi wo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.19,0:01:33.19,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Ato dore dake arukeba ii?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.19,0:01:37.45,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Furikaettemo mou mienai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.45,0:01:41.58,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Kagayaku no wa sugita hi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.58,0:01:49.21,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Onaji toki omoidashite hiku yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.21,0:01:56.47,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Hora kimi to miageteta nagareboshi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.47,0:02:00.43,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Tsurete ikou ano uta wo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.43,0:02:04.47,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Ano toki wo ano yoru wo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.47,0:02:08.52,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Bokura ga iru itsudemo aeru
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.52,0:02:12.52,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Sabishikunai yo soko ni iru kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.52,0:02:14.32,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Wasure wa shinai hibike
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.32,0:02:21.45,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Kono natsukashii senritsu ga
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.45,0:02:25.83,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}bokura ni todoku made
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.03,0:01:00.83,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Kita sedang menuju ke kota itu
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.83,0:01:05.54,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Sambil menyanyikan lagu tak karuan
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.54,0:01:09.42,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}kau berkata "nada apaan itu?” dan tertawa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.42,0:01:14.17,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Kita mengira perjalanan akan terus berlanjut
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.73,0:01:29.19,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Jalan ini dipenuhi dengan kesedihan
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.19,0:01:33.19,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Sampai kapan kita akan terus berjalan?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.19,0:01:37.45,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Berbalik ke belakang, namun sudah tak terlihat
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.45,0:01:41.58,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Masa gemilang dulu t'lah berakhir
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.58,0:01:49.21,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Kita teringat masa-masa yang sama
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.21,0:01:56.47,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Ingat, bintang jatuh yang kita lihat berdua dulu
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.47,0:02:00.43,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Ayo kita bawa lagu itu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.43,0:02:04.47,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Momen itu, malam itu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.47,0:02:08.52,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Kita masih ada di sini, bisa bertemu kapanpun
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.52,0:02:12.52,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Aku tidak kesepian, karena kau ada di sana
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.52,0:02:16.15,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Jangan kau lupakan, teruslah menggema
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:21.45,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}Sampai melodi nostalgia ini
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.45,0:02:25.83,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.5}dapat kita jangkau.
